node.text:
Getting you close to nature in some of the wildest and most remote places on Earth is what @lindbladexp do best. Whether it’s manning the spotting scopes all night to ensure a polar bear sighting or orchestrating a landing at a wildlife site to coincide with sunrise, their expedition teams create thrilling moments for you!

Check out @LindbladExp for wildlife moments and tag #whereiexplore to share your exploration photos with us. 

#LindbladPartner #EarthFocus
Photos by:
1. Michael S. Nolan
2. @richreidphoto
3. @jcalvofoto
5: @colbyoutdoors
